b. The fundamental rights, freedoms and guarantees of citizens;

c. Restrictions and limitations on the rights, freedoms and guarantees of citizens;

d. The election and status of officeholders of bodies that exercise sovereign power, local government officeholders and officeholders in any other constitutional bodies, under the terms of the Constitution and the law;

